snippet.title: Diana and Roma Get in a Fight and Learn to Share
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma are fighting over toys. They make a partition from the construction set and play alone, each on their own side. But the kids get bored. Diana and Roma decide to apologize to each other and learn to share toys to play together. New cartoon for children from Love, Diana!
Thanks for watching!
